Differences between using sessions or JSON Web Tokens for authentication.

Sessions use cookies to create instances('sessions') which stores user information
    that remains peristed until deleted. JWT store user information on  a generated token
   


What does bcrypt do to help us store passwords in a secure manner.

bcrypt hashes passwords scarbles into secure password

How are unit tests different from integration and end-to-end testing.

an end-to-end test runs the entire system.
an integration test runs just two adjoining layers of the system: the integration point.

How Test Driven Development changes the way we write applications and tests.

 makes you to think about the requirements before writing code
